quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  28,51,WE LEKAD WESSELNA LEHUMUL-KAWLE LE’ALLEHUM JETEDHEKKERUNE
  28,52,EL-LEDHINE ‘ATEJNAHUMUL-KITABE MIN KABLIHI HUM BIHI JU’UMINUNE
  28,53,WE ‘IDHA JUTLA ‘ALEJHIM KALU ‘AMENNA BIHI ‘INNEHUL-HEKKU MIN RABBINA ‘INNA KUNNA MIN KABLIHI MUSLIMINE
  28,54,‘ULA’IKE JU’UTEWNE ‘EXHREHUM MERRETEJNI BIMA SEBERU WE JEDRE’UNE BIL-HESENETI ES-SEJJI’ETE WE MIMMA REZEKNAHUM JUNFIKUNE
  28,55,WE ‘IDHA SEMI’UL-LEGWE ‘A’REDU ‘ANHU WE KALU LENA ‘A’MALUNA WE LEKUM ‘A’MALUKUM SELAMUN ‘ALEJKUM LA NEBTEGIL-XHAHILINE
  28,56,‘INNEKE LA TEHDI MEN ‘EHBEBTE WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE JEHDI MEN JESHA’U WE HUWE ‘A’LEMU BIL-MUHTEDINE
  28,57,WE KALU ‘IN NETTEBI’IL-HUDA ME’AKE NUTEHATTEF MIN ‘ERDINA ‘EWELEM NUMEKKIN LEHUM HEREMÆN ‘AMINÆN JUXHBA ‘ILEJHI THEMERATU KULLI SHEJ’IN RIZKÆN MIN LEDUNNA WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  28,58,WE KEM ‘EHLEKNA MIN KARJETIN BETIRET MA’ISHETEHA FETILKE MESAKINUHUM LEM TUSKEN MIN BA’DIHIM ‘ILLA KALILÆN WE KUNNA NEHNUL-WARITHINE
  28,59,WE MA KANE REBBUKE MUHLIKEL-KURA HETTA JEB’ATHE FI ‘UMMIHA RESULÆN JETLU ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATINA WE MA KUNNA MUHLIKIL-KURA ‘ILLA WE ‘EHLUHA DHALIMUNE
  28,60,WE MA ‘UTITUM MIN SHEJ’IN FEMETA’UL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE ZINETUHA WE MA ‘INDEL-LAHI HAJRUN WE ‘EBKA ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  28,61,‘EFEMEN WE’ADNAHU WA’DÆN HESENÆN FEHUWE LAKIHI KEMEN METTA’NAHU META’AL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA THUMME HUWE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI MINEL-MUHDERINE
  28,62,WE JEWME JUNADIHIM FEJEKULU ‘EJNE SHUREKA’IJEL-LEDHINE KUNTUM TEZ’UMUNE
  28,63,KALEL-LEDHINE HEKKA ‘ALEJHIMUL-KAWLU REBBENA HA’UULA’L-LEDHINE ‘EGWEJNA ‘EGWEJNAHUM KEMA GAWEJNA TEBERRE’NA ‘ILEJKE MA KANU ‘IJANA JA’BUDUNE
  28,64,WE KILE ED’U SHUREKA’EKUM FEDE’AWHUM FELEM JESTEXHIBU LEHUM WE RE’EWL-’ADHABE LEW ‘ENNEHUM KANU JEHTEDUNE
  28,65,WE JEWME JUNADIHIM FEJEKULU MADHA ‘EXHEBTUMUL-MURSELINE
  28,66,FE’AMIJET ‘ALEJHIMUL-’ENBA’U JEWME’IDHIN FEHUM LA JETESA’ELUNE
  28,67,FE’EMMA MEN TABE WE ‘AMENE WE ‘AMILE SALIHÆN FE’ASA ‘EN JEKUNE MINEL-MUFLIHINE
  28,68,WE REBBUKE JEHLUKU MA JESHA’U WE JEHTARU MA KANE LEHUMUL-HIJERETU SUBHANEL-LAHI WE TA’ALA ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  28,69,WE REBBUKE JA’LEMU MA TUKINNU SUDURUHUM WE MA JU’LINUNE
  28,70,WE HUWEL-LAHU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE LEHUL-HEMDU FIL-’ULA WEL-’AHIRETI WE LEHUL-HUKMU WE ‘ILEJHI TURXHA’UNE
  28,71,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN XHE’ALEL-LAHU ‘ALEJKUMUL-LEJLE SERMEDÆN ‘ILA JEWMIL-KIJAMETI MEN ‘ILEHUN GAJRU ELLAHI JE’TIKUM BIDIJA’IN ‘EFELA TESMA’UNE
  28,72,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN XHE’ALEL-LAHU ‘ALEJKUMU EN-NEHARE SERMEDÆN ‘ILA JEWMIL-KIJAMETI MEN ‘ILEHUN GAJRU ELLAHI JE’TIKUM BILEJLIN TESKUNUNE FIHI ‘EFELA TUBSIRUNE
  28,73,WE MIN REHMETIHI XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-LEJLE WE EN-NEHARE LITESKUNU FIHI WE LITEBTEGU MIN FEDLIHI WE LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  28,74,WE JEWME JUNADIHIM FEJEKULU ‘EJNE SHUREKA’IJEL-LEDHINE KUNTUM TEZ’UMUNE
  28,75,WE NEZA’NA MIN KULLI ‘UMMETIN SHEHIDÆN FEKULNA HATU BURHANEKUM FE’ALIMU ‘ENNEL-HEKKA LILLAHI WE DELLE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEFTERUNE